### Aegis Assault Game Design ###
1. Rail Shooter
	a. Players	- move horizontal/vertical
	b. Camera	- moves on a rail/path and limits player movement
	c. Enemies	- flies on path or stationary; might shoot
2. Player Experience	- chaotic
3. Core Mechanics		- dodge and shoot
2. Core Game Loop		- get as far as possible without dying to obtain highest score; start from beginning when died
